Something like the "tar" program: glue a bunch of files together into
one big file, and include their names and other metadata.

Info to store for a nondirectory:

path
contents
is-file?
is-link?
file-or-directory-modify-seconds
file-or-directory-permissions

Info to store for a directory:
path
file-or-directory-modify-seconds
file-or-directory-permissions
info for each contained object
